  <span style="color:#070;font-weight:bold">&lt;span</span> <span style="color:#b48">class</span>=<span style="background-color:hsla(0,100%,50%,0.05)"><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span><span style="color:#D20">message-text</span><span style="color:#710">&quot;</span></span><span style="color:#070;font-weight:bold">&gt;</span>
    I had a fantastic sandwich at Primanti's for lunch.
  <span style="color:#070;font-weight:bold">&lt;/span&gt;</span>
